      "passage_index": 11,
      "title": "United States Bankruptcy Court for the Southern District of New York",
      "score": 0.042156411450462415,
      "text": "United States Bankruptcy Court for the Southern District of New York\nThe United States Bankruptcy Court for the Southern District of New York is the United States bankruptcy court within the United States District Court for the Southern District of New York. The Southern District of New York is a major venue for bankruptcy, as it has jurisdiction over the corporate headquarters and major financial institutions located in Manhattan.",
      "score_breakdown": {
