      "passage_index": 0,
      "title": "Dunbar Hospital",
      "score": 0.04213390311254759,
      "text": "Dunbar Hospital\nThe Dunbar Hospital was the first hospital for the black community in Detroit, Michigan. It is located at 580 Frederick Street, and is currently the administrative headquarters of the Detroit Medical Society. It was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1979.",
